,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You are guaranteed that one of the handlers will be invoked after"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"calling this function. When you are done watching the name, just"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_bus_unwatch_name()"},{"type":"text","text":" with the watcher id this function"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"returns."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the name vanishes or appears (for example the application owning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the name could restart), the handlers are also invoked. If the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" that is used for watching the name disconnects, then"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameVanishedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" is invoked since it is no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"possible to access the name."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Another guarantee is that invocations of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameVanishedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" are guaranteed to alternate; that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is, if "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" is invoked then you are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"guaranteed that the next time one of the handlers is invoked, it"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"will be "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameVanishedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":". The reverse is also true."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This behavior makes it very simple to write applications that want"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to take action when a certain "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"#gdbus-watching-names"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Basically, the application should create object proxies in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" and destroy them again (if any) in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameVanishedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/buswatchname(bustype:name:flags:nameappearedhandler:namevanishedhandler:userdata:userdatafreefunc:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/busWatchName(busType:name:flags:nameAppearedHandler:nameVanishedHandler:userData:userDataFreeFunc:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Starts watching "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"name"},{"type":"text","text":" on the bus specified by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"busType"},{"type":"text","text":" and calls"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameAppearedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nameVanishedHandler"},{"type":"text","text":" when the name is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"known to have an owner respectively known to lose its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"owner. Callbacks will be invoked in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"#g-main-context-push-thread-default"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the thread you are calling this function from."}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":